        "subject": "LU-19768 mdd: add changelog users netlink",
        "message": "LU-19768 mdd: add changelog users netlink\n\nAdd a netlink handler for streaming changelog index and\nregistered changelog users from all MDD targets. The data is\ncollected via a callback registered by mdd.ko into obdclass.ko\n(changelog_nl_collect_fn) to avoid a module dependency.\n\nEach entry carries the MDT device name, current changelog index,\nand a list of users with their last-consumed index, idle time,\nand event mask.\n\nChange-Id: I781578719b548c8195761509fb133354b921e04e\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <mdiep@thelustrecollective.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
